<div class="main_content_div">
    <p class="gs_text" style="margin-top:61px;margin-left:35px;margin-right:15px">
        <p class="gs_text">With high visibility to more than 7 million potential customers annually in Downtown Victoria&rsquo;s business and shopping district, a presence at The Bay Centre carries influential weight.</p>

<p class="gs_text">Get noticed in the Centre of Shopping, Business and Events!</p>

<ul class="gs_text">
	<li>Downtown Victoria welcomes daily more than 33,800 employees, thousands of shoppers and visitors.</li>
	<li>We&rsquo;re located in the centre of the shopping district region. Within a 300-metre radius of The Bay Centre, there are over 400 shops and services!</li>
	<li>The Bay Centre is located in an entertainment hub that&rsquo;s the venue for some 15 annual festivals that attract approximately 1 million people - all to our front doors.</li>
	<li>Other centres will say they&rsquo;re &ldquo;steps&rdquo; from Downtown, or &ldquo;close to Downtown&rdquo;, but only The Bay Centre can lay claim to actually being Downtown.</li>
	<li>Steps away from iconic tourist attractions such as the Parliament Buildings, Fairmont Empress, Royal BC Museum and the Inner Harbour &ndash; All within a 10-minute walk from The Bay Centre.</li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>SPECIALTY LEASING &amp; MERCHANDISe RETAIL UNIT (MRU) OPPORTUNITIES</h2>

<p>With over 7 million customer visits per year, The Bay Centre is the premier shopping destination in Downtown Victoria. It is the Centre that is focused on meeting the lifestyle needs of the downtown worker, resident and out of town visitor; those who live, work and play downtown. Whether you&rsquo;re launching a new concept or are already a retailer looking for more exposure, The Bay Centre is the ideal place to launch.</p>

<p>We are always looking for new and original concepts that complement The Bay Centre brand and our guest&rsquo;s shopping experience. For more information on The Bay Centre&rsquo;s In-line Specialty Leasing &amp; MRU Program, please contact Darlene Hollstein, General Manager, at&nbsp;dhollstein@20vic.com.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>PERMANENT LEASING</h2>

<p>The Bay Centre brand is in very good company. The Bay Centre has a proven traffic driving mix of over 90 street front and interior shops comprised of services and amenities such as Passport Canada and GoodLife Fitness, plus key brands like Guess?, Quiksilver, BCBGMAXAZRIA, Club Monaco, L&rsquo;Occitane and many more.</p>

<p>For more information on The Bay Centre&rsquo;s Permanent Leasing Program, please contact Stan Boniferro, Vice-President, Retail Strategy, at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:sboniferro@20VIC.com">sboniferro@20VIC.com</a>.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>Brand Activations &amp; Partnerships</h2>

<p>At The Bay Centre we value innovation and an &ldquo;out of the box&rdquo; approach to enrich our guest&rsquo;s experience. Whether it is hosting an event, touring exhibits, seasonal lounges or other exciting promotional experiences, partnering with The Bay Centre is an active way to reach out to your targeted customer by:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Building top-of-mind awareness</li>
	<li>Generating a positive image</li>
	<li>Introducing or test-market new products or services</li>
	<li>Captivating a receptive audience</li>
	<li>Market penetration into ideal segments</li>
	<li>Developing brand loyalty</li>
</ul>

<p>For more information on The Bay Centre&rsquo;s Brand Activations &amp; Partnership Program, please contact Adrienne Lockstead, Marketing Director, at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:alockstead@20vic.com">alockstead@20vic.com</a>.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>In-Mall Advertising</h2>

<p>Get noticed!&nbsp; Capitalize on high foot traffic to capture a targeted consumer audience through food court television screens, interior and exterior on-site signage, floor decals, specialty wraps, tent cards and more.&nbsp;</p>

<p>For more information on The Bay Centre&rsquo;s In-mall Advertising Program, please contact Neo Traffic at <a href="mailto:sales@neo-traffic.com">sales@neo-traffic.com</a>.</p>

